{"tid":2287263,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"個個都屌難食黃店 有好食嘅介紹吓?","createTime":"2020-11-15T15:04:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T17:29:36.000Z","uid":22471,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"5b2876383b42d9ca1b5067fcaf4671fcf768188e","tid":2287263,"uid":22471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T15:04:55.000Z","msg":"見隔離又喺度屌啲黃店數銀紙<br />\n不如去搵啲真係抵佢地數銀紙嘅老細<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n難食嘅好多都出晒名 eg 渣家軍 龍門<br />\n但想知有無啲唔係好出名但食過好食嘅黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時唔洗排隊都食到好嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n拋磚引玉!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上次食過間觀塘嘅the stadium<br />\n環境幾闊落又唔多人 啲嘢都幾好食<br />\n同行有素食嘅人 都唔會話無嘢揀<br />\n算係選擇幾多 可惜無打開卡無相<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n灣仔又有間burger home (sorry又係無圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個burger熱辣辣又juicy <br />\n抵屌過隔離5guys好多 <br />\n60幾蚊又晒成個set 爽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84e94d1b1416f25ddeb43b6cb6179376f4717eb9","tid":2287263,"uid":211110,"like":8,"dislike":56,"score":-48,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T15:06:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"13142e6d17bb7cb20a04087ac1db93783f8384ee","tid":2287263,"uid":9,"like":19,"dislike":5,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T15:08:16.000Z","msg":"杜文澤介紹個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18afcaffaabf6517f02fe013902f9a81b85490c6","tid":2287263,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T15:09:07.000Z","msg":"燒山囉"},{"pid":"73a265d2acf940407ff02bb9b0afee44d5bc7940","tid":2287263,"uid":14494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T15:09:08.000Z","msg":"好食果D日日排晒長龍, 唔想再多D人等<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1f5871c44e5fc4b33191